title: Win8.1-Pro-9477-(x64)-Pre_RTM-PA-(Zh-Us-Ru)
description:
Here is a new leaked version of Windows Blue 8.1 build 9477 released from August 4,2013

This is a pre RTM version but delivered originaly in Chinese language only.

However it has been recompiled with different parts from the previous 9471 build that we are still seeding.

Russian and English language are also available now and this version is pre-registered 'cause it still work with Public Preview key from june 2013.

Some options may not work perfectly or completely for several reasons 'cause it is a recompiled build but most of them should be functional anyway.

Still as 64 bit version for a final size of 3,19 Go
Coming still with time bomb till January 2014.
This is an evaluation build.

checked,cleared and approved and seeming working quite fine anyway...

See yourself and decide so.

Enjoy and seed,please,thx

kind regards

Note :
We recall you now that we do not accept proxy 'cause our connections are not fast enough for a such possibility,so please,pay attention and do respect this
particularity.
Ty for understanding
